---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  seo={{
    title: "Privacy Policy and Data Protection Practices",
    description: "Read how PraveenTechWorld protects your privacy. Learn what data we collect, how we use cookies, and your rights regarding your personal information.",
  }}
>
  <article class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 dark:prose-invert">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      PraveenTechWorld respects your privacy. This policy explains how we handle
      your information.
    </p>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We do not collect personal information directly. We use standard web
      analytics to understand how visitors use our site, including page views,
      referring sites, and browser type. This data is anonymized and cannot be
      traced back to you.
    </p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use minimal cookies for site functionality, such as storing your theme
      preference (light or dark mode). We do not use tracking cookies,
      advertising cookies, or third-party marketing cookies.
    </p>
    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Analytics data is retained for 26 months before automatic deletion. If you
      contact us via email, we keep your message and contact details only as long
      as needed to address your inquiry, after which they are deleted.
    </p>
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Depending on your location, you may have rights under GDPR or CCPA,
      including the right to access, correct, or delete your data. Since we do
      not collect personal data directly, these rights are generally managed
      through the analytics provider. You can opt out of analytics tracking by
      adjusting your browser settings.
    </p>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We use Vercel for hosting and analytics. Vercel privacy policies apply to
      any data they process on our behalf. We do not use any other third-party
      services that collect personal data.
    </p>
    <h2>Updates</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy as needed. Changes will be posted on this page
      with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes takes effect
      constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy? Email{" "}
      <a href="mailto:hello@praveentechworld.com">hello@praveentechworld.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
